headline.print_headline: Factbox: Tea Party Activist Brat Is Economist and Ayn Rand Fan
headline.main: Factbox: Tea Party Activist Brat Is Economist and Ayn Rand Fan

lead_paragraph: David Brat, who scored a huge political upset with his primary election defeat of House of Representatives Majority Leader Eric Cantor, is a conservative Tea Party Republican and a college professor who has written about the role of religion in economic growth.
